summary:
Day 18. Favorite crack ship?
Honestly? Wonah. I was never an active shipper who, like, made content for the ship, but I was on...
body:
Day 18. Favorite crack ship?

Honestly? Wonah. I was never an active shipper who, like, made content for the ship, but I was on board with it when it came across my dash, so when I learned it was all a wild experiment? I was kind of upset because up until then I just saw it as a cute little ship that people liked the idea of (I’m not upset anymore. I know you guys weren’t doing it maliciously or anything. Don’t worry.). It was kind of funny because the day the episode where Jonah and Walker met aired was the day that the “experiment” was revealed and honestly? Their meeting outsold! It was a cute ass moment, y’all. I was so proud of Jonah for not going off at Walker or doing something dramatic because of Andi. So, yeah, Wonah is a crack ship, but it’s a crack ship I can stand behind.
